OL,7,FA cocaine-fuelled man who beat his
OL,8,Fdisabled father to death after
OL,9,Fapparently mistaking him for an
OL,10,Fintruder has been jailed for his
OL,11,F"unthinkable" murder.
OL,13,FPeter McGarry binged on cocaine and
OL,14,Falcohol before brutally attacking his
OL,15,F76-year-old dad Malcolm McGarry in a
OL,16,F"truly savage beating" at his home in
OL,17,FSutton-in-Ahsfield, Nottinghamshire.
