OL,7,FPolice officers found Mr McGarry in
OL,8,Fthe living room with severe head and
OL,9,Ffacial injuries covered in blood in
OL,10,Fthe early hours of 1 December last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FHis son, 53-year-old Peter McGarry,
OL,14,Fwas arrested at the scene. When told
OL,15,Fby officers he was being arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of murdering his father, he
OL,17,Freplied: "My dad? Are you kidding?"
