OL,7,FA post-mortem examination found Mr
OL,8,FMcGarry, who was partially paralysed
OL,9,Fhaving suffered a stroke in 2013,
OL,10,Fsustained a severe and traumatic brain
OL,11,Finjury along with multiple facial
OL,12,Finjuries, having been repeatedly
OL,13,Fkicked and punched by his son.
OL,15,FNottingham Crown Court heard McGarry
OL,16,Fwas under the influence of cocaine and
OL,17,Falcohol and that he told officers he
OL,18,Fbelieved he had attacked a drug-
OL,19,Fdealing intruder, not his father.
