OL,7,FThe court heard he expressed
OL,8,F"disbelief" following the killing,
OL,9,Fadding he'd had a "loving and close
OL,10,Frelationship" with his father and that
OL,11,Fthey'd been watching football together
OL,12,Fin the hours leading up to the
OL,13,F"unthinkable" incident.
OL,15,FMalcolm McGarry's fiancee, Ruth Todd,
OL,16,Fsaid the effect that Malcolm's death
OL,17,Fhas had is "indescribable."
