OL,7,FShe said: "My son and I walked into
OL,8,FMalcolm's bungalow that night and saw
OL,9,Fhim on the floor with the injuries
OL,10,Fthat Peter had inflicted upon him.
OL,12,F"We have both been having flashbacks
OL,13,Fof that image and I have been
OL,14,Fstruggling to sleep. I don't want to
OL,15,Fleave the house anymore and it has
OL,16,Fleft me feeling very depressed.
OL,18,F"I just miss him as he meant so much
OL,19,Fto me."
