OL,7,FIn his sentencing remarks, Judge
OL,8,FStuart Rafferty KC told McGarry he had
OL,9,Fcarried out a "savage attack" on a man
OL,10,Fwho "never showed you a scrap of
OL,11,Funkindness".
OL,13,FHe added: "It was an avoidable death
OL,14,Fand you have deprived yourself and,
OL,15,Fmore importantly, other people of a
OL,16,Fman of value and great esteem. On this
OL,17,Fnight you exploded.
