OL,7,F"Some people think cocaine is a social
OL,8,Fdrug you can take, put down and not be
OL,9,Faffected by. If this case serves any
OL,10,Fpurpose at all, it is to again point
OL,11,Fout to people ` both those selling it
OL,12,Fand those stupid enough to take it and
OL,13,Fbecome addicted to it ` that cocaine
OL,14,Fis an awful and evil drug.
OL,16,F"Without it, you would not be here."
OL,18,FHe sentenced McGarry, of Alexandra
OL,19,FStreet, Kirkby-in-Ashfield to a life
OL,20,Fsentence, with a minimum of 14 years
OL,21,Fand 123 days.
